propDescriptions.bottomAxis: Indicate which axis to display the bottom of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object XAxisProps
propDescriptions.leftAxis: Indicate which axis to display the left of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object YAxisProps
propDescriptions.rightAxis: Indicate which axis to display the right of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object YAxisProps
propDescriptions.topAxis: Indicate which axis to display the top of the charts. Can be a string (the id of the axis) or an object XAxisProps
